Subject: Re: [T2] rear end hangs low! (no, not mine!)

You need to adjust or more likely replace you torsion bars. Over time they 
sag. If your bus is high mileage I would recommend replacing, the parts are 
only about $200.

After adjusting the originals they tend to break.

